trans-unit.source: Represents an instance of an application in a directory.
trans-unit.target: Represents an instance of an application in a directory.

trans-unit.source: This topic provides descriptions of the declared properties and the navigation properties exposed by the <system>ServicePrincipal</system> entity, as well as the operations that you can call on it.
trans-unit.target: This topic provides descriptions of the declared properties and the navigation properties exposed by the <system>ServicePrincipal</system> entity, as well as the operations that you can call on it.
